short.ar: قم بتصدير قوائم المتابعين والمتابَعين على انستغرام بسهولة إلى CSV أو Excel مع IG Export.
short.am: በIG Export አማካኝነት የእርስዎን የInstagram ተከታዮች እና የሚከተሉት ዝርዝሮችን በቀላሉ ወደ CSV ወይም Excel ያውጡ።

long.am,bg,bn,ca,gu,hi,hr,hu,id,lt,lv,ml,mr,m:
Export Instagram Followers/Following List to Excel
IG Export can help you export Instagram followers or following list to a  CSV file.

🖖  KEY FEATURES:

Export millions of  records in minutes.
✓ Export followers from Instagram
✓ Export following list from Instagram
✓ Extract user profile, including follower and following count, biography, public Email, etc.

🔎  HOW DOES IT WORK:

Using Instagram's official API to export data.
1. Enter Instagram Username
2. Select Export type: FOLLOWERS or FOLLOWING
3. Click Export Button
Free user can export the first 500 records.
Paid user can export without limits.

* Coming soon :Select Include user profile in the Extension Setting if you want to export the user profile. This feature will take longer as each user needs to request data. 

🔒  USAGE POLICY

No password required. 
All the data you export is processed locally, so no one knows what you exported.
Read our Privacy Policy: https://www.igtools.store/privacy

📖  FAQ
If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us at joahyi7@gmail.com.
long.en,en_AU:
🖖 KEY FEATURES:

- Export Followers and Following Lists: Effortlessly export millions of records in minutes, streamlining your social media management.
- User-Friendly Navigation: Our extension features a convenient navigation bar for easy access to all functionalities, enhancing your experience while managing your Instagram data.

🔎 HOW DOES IT WORK:

- Utilizing Instagram's official API to export data securely and efficiently.
- Free users can export the first 500 records.
- Paid users enjoy unlimited exports for only $9.99!

🔒 USAGE POLICY:

- No password required for operation.
- All exported data is processed locally on your device, ensuring your privacy—no one knows what you exported.
